data.description: Kings Lake is an established neighborhood located less than 10 minutes from downtown 5th Ave South and the Pier which offers low HOA fees as well as walking trials, biking paths and a tennis/pickleball court.  This Southeastern exposure home situated at the rear of the neighborhood offers a traditional floor plan with a living/dining room and a separate oversized kitchen with breakfast room and family room that all hinges on off the gracious screened pool and lanai area.  Split bedrooms and baths give privacy for guests or family members.  The kitchen boasts an enormous laundry room and walk in pantry.  Ready for ones personal touch or updating, this home is priced to sell!
